{"id": "rios007", "name": "Audio_YazawaRI_495_09_06", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Wait, Rin... Maybe we shouldn't do this...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Eh? Didn't we agree already?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It's okay if you know, but another person...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Don't worry! Katsuya promised me that he wouldn't tell anyone!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I trust Rin... but... won't he think I'm weird? I'm clearly an Architect...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Don't worry, he's a good person... Katsuya! Here!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Ay, Ay-ya!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin! I finally found you. I've never been here before... Your parents aren't gonna pop out of nowhere, are they?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Relax, they're busy. You nervous? Heehee.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "No!\nSo, by your side... that's...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It-It's... I...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Wah! You're really like a person?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hey, she's a little timid. Don't frighten her.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Aren't I the one who's frightened?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hmph. Whatevs.\nUnit 10, this is Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Hel... Hello...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Eh... Hello.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... Hey, what's going on?</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Hahaha!!\nYou two are so embarrassed!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "That... that's normal! I've never really spoken with an Architect! Plus, with this weird kind of...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya! How could you? That's so rude! Don't you forget, that flower is only living because of Unit 10's help!\n<font size=\"1.6\">Without it, we'd never be together...</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "That's true... Thank you, uh... Unit 10.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It's-It's nothing...\n... Is the flower, is it doing well?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin planted it at the Academy. It's pretty healthy.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Really? Excellent, I've been worried! If you want a flower to blossom even more vigorously, you can carefully remove the peripheral buds. That way the flower bud will get enough nutrients. Besides getting some sun, you also want to pay attention to the wind and pests, then it'll grow even better...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Uh...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Okay, okay, stop!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Ah! I...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "It's always like this! You just keep talking about flowers and plants, just like my dad...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "S-Sorry... My memory unit... there's a lot of info on plants and horticulture stored on it... <font size=\"1.6\">If I'm not careful...</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...<i>*smirk*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya? What's up with that smile?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Nothing, I just think...\n... You're very interesting, Unit 10.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I'm... interesting.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Yup. I thought you'd be more like a robot, but after hearing you speak... it kinda changed my mind. No wonder you became friends with Rin.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...! Mr. Katsuya...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hey, whatta you mean \"no wonder\"?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "It's nothing... Unit 10, very nice to meet you.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Indeed!\nI'm... It's so nice to meet you as well!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "待って、凛……やっぱりやめよう……？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え？なんで今更。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛ならいいけど……他の人がこのことを知ったら……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "大丈夫！克也約束してくれたもん！\n10号機のこと、絶対に誰にも言わないって！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛のことは信じたいけど……でも……私のこと変だって思わないかな？\n私アーキテクトなのに……なのに……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "大丈夫！\n克也はそんなやつじゃないよ！\n……克也！こっち！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "お、おう！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛！やっと見つけた！\nこんなところに来るのは初めてだからさ……\nお父さんお母さんが急に現れたりしないよな？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "大丈夫！2人は今仕事中だから。\nなに？緊張してるの？クスクス……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "んなわけねーだろ！\nえっと、じゃあ、隣にいるのが……その……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あ、あの……私……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "うわ！マジで人間みたいだ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ちょっと！\nこの子気が弱いんだから驚かさないであげて！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……驚かされたのは俺なんだけど。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ふん！だ。\n10号機、この人が克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あの……はっはじめまして……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……えっと……はじめまして。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……おい！\nどうすればいいんだよ？</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……あはっ！あはははは！！\nすんごい気まずい空気が流れてる！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "んなっ……！あ、当たり前だろ！？\n俺、アーキテクトとこんな風に会話したことなんかないんだから！\nしかもこんなおかしな……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！\nおかしいって何？失礼なこと言わないで！\nあの花だって、10号機のおかげで今も元気なんだからね！\n<font size=\"1.6\">あの花がなかったら、私たちだって付き合ってなかったと思うし……</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "確かにそうだな……えっと、ありがとう……10号機。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "い、いえ……そんな……\n……あのお花……どうだった？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛がアカデミーに植え替えたんだ。\n今でも元気だよ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "そっか……よかった！私、心配してたの！\nあっ……もしもっとお花を元気にしたければ、側芽を取ってあげるといいよ。\nそうすれば、つぼみに十分な養分が回るから……\nでも気を付けて慎重にね。\nあとは、風通しのいいところにおいてあげて、虫にも注意して……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……あー……っと……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……ストップ！ストーップ！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あっ！私……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "まーた10号機の悪い癖が出た！\n花とか草とかの話になると止まらなくなるんだから。\nお父さんと一緒……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "ごっごめんなさい……\n私のメモリーには植物関連の知識がいっぱい保存されてて……<font size=\"1.6\">だから思わず……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ぶはっ……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！今こっそり笑ったでしょ！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ちが……っ、違うって。\nただ……面白いヤツだなって思ってさ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私が……面白い？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "あぁ。\nもっと……こうロボットっぽいのかと思ってたけど、話してみて考えが変わったよ。\nどうりで凛と友達になるわけだ……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！克也さん……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ちょっと！「どうりで」ってどういう意味！？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "いや？\n10号機、これからよろしくな。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……うん！\nあなたたちに出会えて私……嬉しい！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "等一下，凜……還是算了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "欸？我們不是說好了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜的話沒關係，但要是其他人知道了……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒問題的啦！克也答應過我，不會把妳的事情說出去的！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我相信凜……可是……他會不會覺得我很怪？明明是建造者還……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心，他是個很好的人……克也！這裡！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "呀、呀啊！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜！總算找到妳了，我沒來過這種地方……妳爸媽不會突然出現吧？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心吧，他們在忙。你很緊張嗎？嘻嘻。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "才不會！\n那，妳旁邊的……就是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那、那個……我……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇！真的像人一樣？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，她有點膽小，你不要嚇到人家了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……我才是被嚇到的那個吧？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哼，不理你了。\n十號機，他就是克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "你……你好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……妳好。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……喂，現在是怎樣？</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……哈哈哈！！\n你們超尷尬的！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這……這很正常吧！我從來沒跟建造者好好說過話啊！而且還是這種奇怪的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！什麼奇怪，太失禮了吧！別忘了，那朵花也是有十號機幫忙才能活下來的唷！\n<font size=\"1.6\">要不是它我們也不會在一起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這倒是……謝謝妳了，呃……十號機。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不會……\n……那朵花，後來還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "被凜種在學院裡了，還蠻健康的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真的嗎？太好了，我好擔心！啊，如果想讓花朵開的更有精神，可以小心地摘除側芽，花蕾就會有充足的養分。除了曬太陽，也要注意通風和除蟲，會讓它長得更好……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "啊！我……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳又來了！講到花花草草就停不下來，跟我爸一個樣……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "對、對不起……我的記憶體儲存了許多植物、園藝相關的知識……<font size=\"1.6\">一不小心就……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "噗……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！你在偷笑對吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒有啦，我只是覺得……\n……妳還蠻有趣的嘛，十號機。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……有趣？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯。我還以為會更像機器人一點，但說過話之後……稍微有點改觀了。難怪妳會和凜變成朋友……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！克也先生……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，「難怪」是什麼意思啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒什麼……十號機，很高興認識妳。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯！\n我也……很高興認識你們！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "잠깐, Rin... 그래도 역시...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "엥? 이미 그렇게 하기로 다 얘기했잖아?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin은 괜찮지만, 다른 사람이 알게 되는 것은...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "괜찮다니까! Katsuya도 약속했어! 절대로 네 일에 대해서 입도 뻥긋하지 않을 거야!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "나는 Rin을 믿어... 하지만... 그 사람은 날 이상하게 생각하지 않을까? 어쨌든 나는 아키텍트이니까...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "안심해. 엄청 착한 애야.... Katsuya! 여기야!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아, 잠깐!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin!, 드디어 찾았네. 이런 곳엔 처음 와봐서... 네 부모님이 갑자기 나타나시거나 그러는 건 아니겠지?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "안심해. 지금 일하고 계시니까.\n지금 긴장하고 있는 거야? 하하.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아니야!\n저, 네 옆에 있는 게... 그...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "저, 저기... 저는...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "으앗! 진짜 사람 같잖아!?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "야! 놀래키지 말라고! 얘가 얼마나 겁이 많은데.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...지금 여기서 놀랜 사람은 나 아닌가...?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "흥! 그냥 내가 말을 말아야지...\n10호기, 얘가 내가 얘기했던 Katsuya야!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아... 안녕하세요...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...아... 안녕.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">.....야, 이제 어떡해야 하지?</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...푸하하하!\n둘이 완전 어색해하고 있어!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "이... 이게 정상이라고! 난 여지껏 아키텍트랑 얘기해 본 적이 없단 말이야! 게다가 이런 이상한...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya! 이상하다니, 실례잖아! 그 꽃도 10호기가 도와줬기 때문에 잘 자랄 수 있었다고 말했던 거, 벌써 까먹었어?\n<font size=\"1.6\">얘가 아니었으면 우리도 이렇게 사귀지 못 했다고...</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그건... 알았어.\n...고, 고마워, 저... 10호기.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아, 아닙니다...\n...그 꽃은 무사한 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin이 교내에 잘 심어놨어. \n지금도 잘 자라고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그렇습니까? 정말 다행이네요. 엄청 걱정했었는데! 아, 만약 꽃을 피우게 하려면 주의해야 할 점이 더 늘어나게 됩니다. 근처에 난 다른 싹 부분을 조심스럽게 제거해 주시고 태양을 쬐게 하는 것 이외에도 통풍이라든가 벌레들이 있는지도 확인해주셔야 해요. 이것만 잘 지키면 훨씬 더 잘 자랄 수 있게...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...아, 그게...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...오케이, 오케이~ 스톱!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아! 나는...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그 버릇 또 나왔네! 꽃 얘기만 하면 멈출 줄을 모른다니까. 우리 아빠처럼...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "미, 미안해... 내 메모리에 식물과 원예와 관련된 지식들이 많이 저장돼있어서... <font size=\"1.6\">나도 모르게...</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "풉....\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya! 왜 웃는 건데!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아니야! 그저...\n...네가 상당히 재미있다고 느껴져서, 10호기.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "내가... 재밌다고요?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "응. 난 네가 훨씬 더 로봇에 가까울 줄 알았는데, 대화를 나눠보니... 내 생각이 조금은 변한 것 같기도. \n 어쩐지 네가 Rin과 어떻게 친구가 될 수 있었는가 했더니...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...! Katsuya 씨...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "야! [어쩐지]라니? 무슨 뜻인데!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아무것도 아니야... 10호기, 만나서 정말 반가워.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...네!\n저도... 여러분을 알게 돼서 너무 기쁩니다!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "等一下，凜……還是算了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "欸？我們不是說好了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜的話沒關係，但要是其他人知道了……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒問題的啦！克也答應過我，不會把妳的事情說出去的！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我相信凜……可是……他會不會覺得我很怪？明明是建造者還……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心，他是個很好的人……克也！這裡！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "呀、呀啊！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜！總算找到妳了，我沒來過這種地方……妳爸媽不會突然出現吧？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心吧，他們在忙。你很緊張嗎？嘻嘻。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "才不會！\n那，妳旁邊的……就是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那、那個……我……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇！真的像人一樣？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，她有點膽小，你不要嚇到人家了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……我才是被嚇到的那個吧？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哼，不理你了。\n十號機，他就是克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "你……你好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……妳好。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……喂，現在是怎樣？</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……哈哈哈！！\n你們超尷尬的！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這……這很正常吧！我從來沒跟建造者好好說過話啊！而且還是這種奇怪的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！什麼奇怪，太失禮了吧！別忘了，那朵花也是有十號機幫忙才能活下來的唷！\n<font size=\"1.6\">要不是它我們也不會在一起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這倒是……謝謝妳了，呃……十號機。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不會……\n……那朵花，後來還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "被凜種在學院裡了，還蠻健康的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真的嗎？太好了，我好擔心！啊，如果想讓花朵開的更有精神，可以小心地摘除側芽，花蕾就會有充足的養分。除了曬太陽，也要注意通風和除蟲，會讓它長得更好……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "啊！我……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳又來了！講到花花草草就停不下來，跟我爸一個樣……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "對、對不起……我的記憶體儲存了許多植物、園藝相關的知識……<font size=\"1.6\">一不小心就……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "噗……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！你在偷笑對吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒有啦，我只是覺得……\n……妳還蠻有趣的嘛，十號機。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……有趣？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯。我還以為會更像機器人一點，但說過話之後……稍微有點改觀了。難怪妳會和凜變成朋友……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！克也先生……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，「難怪」是什麼意思啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒什麼……十號機，很高興認識妳。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯！\n我也……很高興認識你們！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "等一下，凛……还是算了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "欸？我们不是说好了吗？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛的话没关系，但要是其他人知道了……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "没问题的啦！克也答应过我，不会把妳的事情说出去的！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我相信凛……可是……他会不会觉得我很怪？明明是建造者还……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心，他是个很好的人……克​​也！这里！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "呀、呀啊！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛！总算找到妳了，我没来过这种地方……妳爸妈不会突然出现吧？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心吧，他们在忙。你很紧张吗？嘻嘻。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "才不会！\n那，妳旁边的……就是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那、那个……我……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇！真的像人一样？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，她有点胆小，你不要吓到人家了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……我才是被吓到的那个吧？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哼，不理你了。\n十号机，他就是克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "你……你好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……妳好。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……喂，现在是怎样？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……哈哈哈！ ！\n你们超尴尬的！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "这……这很正常吧！我从来没跟建造者好好说过话啊！而且还是这种奇怪的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！什么奇怪，太失礼了吧！别忘了，那朵花也是有十号机帮忙才能活下来的唷！\n<font size=\"1.6\">要不是它我们也不会在一起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "这倒是……谢谢妳了，呃……十号机。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不会……\n……那朵花，后来还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "被凛种在学院里了，还蛮健康的。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真的吗？太好了，我好担心！啊，如果想让花朵开的更有精神，可以小心地摘除侧芽，花蕾就会有充足的养分。除了晒太阳，也要注意通风和除虫，会让它长得更好……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……呃……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "啊！我……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳又来了！讲到花花草草就停不下来，跟我爸一个样……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "对、对不起……我的记忆体储存了许多植物、园艺相关的知识……<font size=\"1.6\">一不小心就……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "噗……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！你在偷笑对吧？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "没有啦，我只是觉得……\n……妳还蛮有趣的嘛，十号机。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……有趣？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯。我还以为会更像机器人一点，但说过话之后……稍微有点改观了。难怪妳会和凛变成朋友……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！克也先生……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "喂，「难怪」是什么意思啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "没什么……十号机，很高兴认识妳。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯！\n我也……很高兴认识你们！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}